data.description: I welcome you to seize the opportunity to own a slice of luxury living. Schedule your showing today and discover the hidden gem awaiting you! The Interior Charm to this 3 bedroom 3 bathroom is a must see.   Location is everything,  Situated in a highly sought-after area. This home located near the heart of the city. But, still has the small town feeling that Peyton/Falcon offers while being away from the hectic hustling and bustling.   Being part of Woodmen Hills water district means you get to enjoy 2 Rec centers, complete with workout facilities, indoor & outdoor pools and so much more!  Embrace the simplicity of a low-maintenance modest size fenced yard.   Schedule your showing today and make this home yours before it's gone!  It's better than new and is turnkey ready for you!
